title: Drunk streamer looking for people to hang with

embed.description: OCE] Challanger drinker, silver league player

body:
Hey guys,
Names vicelore Im a 33 year old League player, I stream nightly from 9 PM AEST till after midnight, Currently making the climb from Silver to gold playing mostly jungle.

Every night im having a few beers, chilling, climbing and listening to music and chatting with everyone on twitch, normally with a duo from a 300 member Discord I run.
Id love to meet some more people on twitch, If this sound up your alley, pop by and say Hi.

Sub or donate and ill even skull my current beer to show you how much I care.

Cheers vicelore
